<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q27_v15" title="Q27_v15" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceA</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Registro del caso:</p><p>Una marca de arroz se vende siempre en paquetes idénticos. En un diagrama se muestra que 3 paquetes de este arroz corresponden en total a 750 g de arroz.</p>
    <p>
      <img src="requiere_nueva_imagen.png" alt="Diagrama con dos rectángulos: el de la izquierda contiene el texto '3 paquetes' y el de la derecha el texto '750 g de arroz'. Una flecha horizontal apunta del rectángulo '3 paquetes' al rectángulo '750 g de arroz', indicando que 3 paquetes de arroz pesan en total 750 g." />
    </p>
    <p>Si <m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:math> es el número de paquetes y <m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:math> la masa total en gramos, ¿cuál de las siguientes expresiones describe de manera coherente la relación mostrada en el diagrama?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac><m:mn>750</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mi>p</m:mi>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si 3 paquetes pesan 750 g, entonces 1 paquete pesa 750 ÷ 3 = 250 g. Por lo tanto, p paquetes pesan 250p g, y eso es exactamente igual a (750/3)p.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>750</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mi>p</m:mi>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta expresión asigna a cada paquete una masa de 3/750 g. Si p = 3, resulta R(3) = (3/750) × 3 = 9/750 = 0,012 g, pero el enunciado dice que 3 paquetes pesan 750 g.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo>
            <m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>750</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si p = 3, esta expresión da R(3) = 3 + 750 = 753, pero el diagrama muestra que 3 paquetes corresponden exactamente a 750 g, no a 753 g.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo>
            <m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>750</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si p = 3, esta expresión da R(3) = 3 − 750 = −747, y una masa total no puede ser negativa. Además, el enunciado indica que 3 paquetes pesan 750 g.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la información del diagrama</strong></p>
            <p>El diagrama indica que 3 paquetes corresponden a 750 g de arroz.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular la masa de 1 paquete</strong></p>
            <p>Como los paquetes son idénticos, la masa de un paquete se obtiene dividiendo 750 g entre 3:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>750</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>250</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces, 1 paquete pesa 250 g.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Expresar la masa total de p paquetes</strong></p>
            <p>Si cada paquete pesa 250 g, entonces p paquetes pesan:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Como <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>750</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> es igual a 250, también se puede escribir:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>750</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar las opciones con p = 3</strong></p>
            <p>Opción A:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>750</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>750</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Opción B:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>750</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mn>750</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Eso no es 750 g.</p>
            <p>Opción C:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>750</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>753</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Eso no es 750 g.</p>
            <p>Opción D:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>750</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>747</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Eso no es una masa válida y tampoco coincide con 750 g.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión que describe coherentemente la relación mostrada es la alternativa A:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>750</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>